data.description: Welcome home to 13731 Duxton Dr in the lovely neighborhood of The Villages of Longmeadow! This stunning 2-car garage, 5 bedroom, 2.5 bath residence offers a perfect blend of style and comfort.  As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the warm and inviting ambiance created by the beautiful wood flooring throughout the first floor.  The spacious and airy layout provides ample room for relaxation and entertainment. The kitchen has ample counter space, pantry, and cabinet space with eat-in kitchen. Upstairs, the primary bedroom and additional four bedrooms are generously sized, offering flexibility for a growing family or the option to create a home office or flex space.  New microwave. Hot water heater is 2 years old. Irrigation system. The Longmeadow Community offers a range of amenities, including a community pool, clubhouse, and playground. This is a highly sought after community offering peaceful convenience. We are close to major commuter routes, shopping, and other activities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this home your own and experience the best of Chester living.No home sale Contingencies. Schedule your showing today!
